Player uses attacks with hotbar

Enemy attacks (player aggro is chance)

attacking creatures

add item called bag
bag can store specific item, but more
small bag can store the current items stack size x2
medium = x3
large = x4
taking oout items is as easy as going to bag, pressing e(empty), and putting amount to remove
adding items is as easy as going to bag and pressing f(fill) to add amount of items to bag


